# 统一跨平台换行符：所有文本文件以 LF 存储，抑制 Windows 上
# `core.autocrlf=true` 触发的 "LF will be replaced by CRLF" 警告。
* text=auto eol=lf

# 明确几类二进制，避免被当成文本处理
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.docx binary
*.xlsx binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.duckdb binary
*.duckdb.wal binary
